| **Navigation** | Expo Router | v3 | File-based, deep links automatic |
| **Animations** | React Native Reanimated | v3 | UI thread — 60fps mandatory |
| **Gestures** | React Native Gesture Handler | v2 | Works with Reanimated v3 |
| **Server state** | TanStack Query | v5 | MMKV persister for offline |
| **Client state** | Zustand | v4 | UI state, gesture state |
| **Local storage** | MMKV | Latest | 10× AsyncStorage. Encrypted. Sync reads. |
| **Backend** | Supabase | Latest | ap-south-1 (Mumbai). PostgreSQL 15. |
| **Edge Functions** | Deno TypeScript | Via Supabase | RE module, events, onboarding, health |
| **Push notifications** | OneSignal | Free tier | Scheduling, segmentation built in |
| **Analytics** | PostHog | Free tier | 1M events/month free |
| **Error monitoring** | Sentry | Free tier | 5K errors/month free |
| **Weather** | OpenWeatherMap | Free tier | 1K calls/day free |
| **Image CDN** | Cloudinary | Free tier | 25GB bandwidth/month |
